<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,406,622,647]" pageId="23" pageNumber="24">DISTRIBUTION</emphasis>
: Northern Borneo [Kenokok, Mt Kinabalu] (
<figureCitation box="[911,1008,623,647]" captionStart="FIGURE 137–139" captionStartId="108.[151,249,1637,1660]" captionTargetBox="[151,1436,193,1616]" captionTargetId="figure-104@108.[151,1436,193,1616]" captionTargetPageId="108" captionText="FIGURE 137–139. Distribution of Oriental and Australasian Leptomorphus. 137. L. chaseni (red circle), L. ornatus (red triangle), L. tabatius (black square), L. tagbanua (blue star), L. titiwangsensis (black circle). 138. Species described by Papp &amp; Ševčík 2011. L. alienus (red triangle), L. ascutellatus (red star), L. baramensis (black triangle), L. gunungmuluensis (purple square), L. longipes (blue circle), L. matilei (yellow star), L. papua (black square), L. utarensis (red circle). 139. Expanded view of northern Borneo showing distribution of L. baramensis, L. gunungmuluensis, and L. longipes." pageId="23" pageNumber="24">Fig. 137</figureCitation>
), 
<quantity box="[1028,1147,623,647]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="23" pageNumber="24" unit="m" value="1000.0">1000 masl</quantity>
